## 10) Notes for implementation with Next.js

- Dùng route segments theo pattern:
  - `app/(public)/...`
  - `app/(app)/app/w/[workspaceId]/...`
  - `app/(admin)/admin/...`
- Dùng middleware/client guard để:
  - nếu chưa login -> về `/auth/login`
  - nếu role mismatch -> show page `403`
- Dùng shared fetch client + centralized error parser.

